TextEng: I'd like to ask you some questions.
Me is wanting ask questions from you.
Text: 나 너한테 물어보고 싶은 거 있어.

TextEng: Goodbye.
Why did Karathis insist on going in alone?
Do you know where the others might be?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> What can you tell me of Alhelor?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 알헬러에 대해 뭘 말해줄 수 있어요?

TextEng: What's going on in Port Llast?
Text: 라스트 항구에서 무슨 일이 일어나고 있나요?

TextEng: Why Karathis go in first without friends?
Text: 왜 카라디스 혼자 먼저 들어갔어? 친구들 없이?

TextEng: Me looks for other boys.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me talks with Alhelor. What you knows?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 알헬러랑 얘기해. 너 뭐 알아?

TextEng: What stuff happen in Port Llast?
Why did Karathis need your help then?
Text: 그럼 왜 카라디스는 당신의 도움이 필요했죠?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Are you sure the beast was Karathis?
Why Karathis wants you and friends coming?
Text: 왜 카라디스 너랑 친구들 오라고 했어?

TextEng: You know where Urth could be?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> <StartAction>Ask where the werewolf's den is.</Start>
How about Bran? Where would he go?
What did he say?
What says he to you?
Can you tell me about your experience with the Black Wolf?
Text: 검은 늑대와의 경험에 대해 말해줄 수 있어요?

TextEng: Me wants to know what happen 'tween Black Wolf and you.
Text: 나 검은 늑대랑 너 사이에 무슨 일 있었는지 알고 싶어.

TextEng: Let me ask you about something else.
Me changes subject, ask other stuffs.
Text: 나 다른 주제로 바꿔, 다른 거 물어봐.

TextEng: Can I ask you some directions?
Can me gets told where places is?
I need to find a temple.
Is there someplace I can buy equipment?
Text: 장비를 살 수 있는 곳이 있나요?

TextEng: Me wants temple.
Me runs low on supplies. Me can buy?
Text: 나 물건 거의 떨어져. 나 살 수 있어?

TextEng: Actually, I'd rather ask you about something else.
Me have other question.
Maybe you can tell me where to look for Geth?
Text: 게스를 어디서 찾아야 할지 말해줄 수 있어요?

TextEng: What about Sir Karathis? Where would he be?
I spoke with Neurik. He said I should see you.
Me gets told by Neurik to talks with you.
Who is Alhelor?
Who this Alhelor?
Neurik? Alhelor? Sleeping troubles? Did I miss something?
Text: 뉴릭? 알헬러? 수면 장애? 제가 뭘 놓친 건가요?

TextEng: Neurik? Alhelor? Sleeping troubles? Me not understand.
Text: 뉴릭? 알헬러? 잠 문제? 나 이해 못 해.

TextEng: Who are you?
Who you be?
Where was the Black Wolf's cave again?
Me ask where Black Wolf cave is, yuh?
Text: 나 검은 늑대 동굴 어딘지 물어봐, 응?

TextEng: You knows where Urth is?
Maybe Bran? Where he be?
Um... Geth? You know where is?
Me looks for Sir Karathis? Where he go?
Text: 나 카라디스 경 찾아? 어디로 갔어?

TextEng: Nope, me not wants that.
No thanks.
Yeah, you tells me.
Yes, tell me.
You tells me about werewolf you meets.
Text: 너 만난 늑대인간에 대해 말해 줘.

TextEng: Tell me about your encounter with the werewolf.
What werewolf? What you says?
What's this about a werewolf?
You helps sell what?
Werewolf remedies?
What you goings to do, now?
What do you plan on doing now?
Yeah, you is useless, for sure.
Yes, you're pretty useless, all right.
You makes money when you helps Alhelor, huh?
Text: 너 알헬러 도울 때 돈 벌었지, 응?

TextEng: You must have made some money helping Alhelor, no?
Then you is dumb kid! Hah!
Then you're an idiot. Hah!
Is good. You gives me coin and you nots get hurt.
Text: 좋아. 너 나한테 돈 주면 너 다치지 않아.

TextEng: Good. Hand over the coin, then, and be quick about it.
Me thinks you should go, then, maybe.
Text: 나 생각에 너 그럼 가야 할 것 같아, 아마.

TextEng: I think you should move on, then.
You kids me? You not finds way out of town! Ha ha!
Text: 너 농담이지? 너 마을 밖도 못 나가! 하하!

TextEng: Are you kidding? You couldn't find your way out of town!
Text: 농담하는 거예요? 당신 마을 밖도 못 나갈걸요!

TextEng: Here... me gives 100 gold to helps out.
Here... 100 gold to help you out.
Okays. You do that.
You do that.
Maybe you coulds sell stuff now?
Text: 지금 물건 팔 수도 있지 않아?

TextEng: Maybe you should open your own shop?
Hah! Me jokes! You never does that!
Text: 하! 나 농담이야! 너 절대 못 해!

TextEng: Hah! I was joking! As if you could ever do it!
Text: 하! 농담이에요! 당신이 할 수 있을 리가!

TextEng: Who this Neurik?
Who is this Neurik?
Why you not talks about it?
Text: 왜 너 그거 얘기 안 해?

TextEng: Why can't you talk about it?
Text: 왜 그것에 대해 말할 수 없나요?

TextEng: Who this Neurik?
Who is this Neurik?
Why you not talks about it?
Text: 왜 너 그거 얘기 안 해?

TextEng: Why can't you talk about it?
Text: 왜 그것에 대해 말할 수 없나요?

TextEng: You tells me where Alhelor live.
Text: 너 알헬러 어디 사는지 말해 줘.

TextEng: Tell me where this Alhelor lives.
Ander... Alhelor really be Black Wolf.
Ander... Alhelor is really the Black Wolf.
You just says if you seen him since he go.
Text: 너 떠난 뒤로 그를 봤는지만 말해 줘.

TextEng: Just tell me if you've seen him since he left.
Text: 떠난 뒤로 그를 봤는지만 말해 주세요.

TextEng: Me knows it sound funny, but me gets to bottom of this soon.
Text: 나 이거 우스운 소리인 거 알지만, 나 곧 진상 밝혀낼 거야.

TextEng: I know it sounds strange, but I will get to the bottom of this.
Text: 이상하게 들리는 거 알지만, 진상을 밝혀낼 겁니다.

TextEng: Me not jokes, Ander. Me want to warns you.
Text: 나 농담 아니야, 앤더. 나 너한테 경고하고 싶었어.

TextEng: I'm not joking, Ander. I wanted to warn you.
Who you?
Who are you?
